    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>breaded egg[s] </strong>to a<strong> baking paper</strong>-lined baking tray and put the tray in the oven for 22-25 min, or until the sausage is cooked through – this is your <strong>spiced scotch egg</strong></p><p>Meanwhile, combine your <strong>tomato ketchup</strong> and <strong>sriracha </strong>in a bowl<strong> </strong>– this is your <strong>spicy ketchup</strong></p>",
